Name: Forum Affiliate Manager
Description: Easily manage your forum's affiliates.
Author: Spencer Swords
Authorsite: http://community.mybb.com/user-23387.html
Version: 1.1
Compatibility: 1.6.x
Files: 2
Database changes: 1 new table.

Installation:
Upload ./files/inc/plugins/affiliates.php to ./inc/plugins/
Upload ./files/inc/languages/english/affiliates.lang.php to ./inc/languages/english/
Upload ./files/inc/languages/english/admin/config_affiliates.lang.php to ./inc/languages/english/admin/
Upload ./files/uploads/affiliates to ./uploads/ and CHMOD to 777.

Go into your Admin CP > Plugins > Install and Activate

Upgrading:
Upload and overwrite existing ./files/inc/plugins/affiliates.php to ./inc/plugins/
Upload and overwrite existing ./files/inc/languages/english/affiliates.lang.php to ./inc/languages/english/


Change log:
03/12/2011 - Added missing affiliates upload folder.
03/13/2011 - Fixed the issue regarding visiting the affiliate's website.
03/18/2011 - New features: Block certain usergroups from viewing the affiliates bar; And specify where you want the affiliates bar to be displayed - either in the header, or footer. Fixes: Improved error handling.